{"tid":982335,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴膠】無懼危險　巴士迷衝馬路　只為搭呢款車？","createTime":"2019-01-15T04:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T19:05:02.000Z","uid":225464,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3907f22915f6a47b8e453c62b3e57da5e83cd5","tid":982335,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"無懼危險　巴士迷衝馬路　只為搭呢款車？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/bkn-20190115100232771-0115_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190115%2Fbkn-20190115100232771-0115_00822_001.html&d=a6jwj76mG8mcAc9%2FaZOaerZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c9581ba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/bkn-20190115100232771-0115_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190115/photo/bkn-20190115100232771-0115_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190115103325\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190115100232771-0115_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190115103325&h=2c74bfc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為咗心愛嘅巴士，可以去到幾盡？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴士迷對巴士的喜愛程度，有時會令人感到困擾。近日就有人為搭上「心頭好」，將生死置之度外？<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」的片段可見，星期日（13日）上午約10時半，有巴士正準備駛入龍翔道近港鐵黃大仙站附近的巴士站時，驚覺有一名青年男子正在馬路狂奔截車。<br />\n<br />\n車長直言該青年「黐線」，並將青年「砵」回行人路。待青年終排隊搭上千辛萬苦盼來的愛車後，他即時解釋︰「我等咗好耐先等到呢架車呀，一架十二米（巴士車身長度）都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n不過司機卻沒理會這份激動之情︰「你冇嘢呀，走出馬路，X你老母咁樣害人，坐番入去唔好同我傾偈，最憎就係呢啲人」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民批評巴士迷做法危險︰「唔好累死人啦」、「有車你就好坐啦揀揀揀」；有人則認出青年，指其平時「幾好禮貌，係有份我哋理解唔到嘅執着」。"},{"pid":"df8ce8b9057a4abf1e1b181cb9ff1f75a09a116c","tid":982335,"uid":137725,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:03:43.000Z","msg":"啲巴士控都幾可愛"},{"pid":"6067242cf194be8781f79bda4b59f70ec5934006","tid":982335,"uid":74171,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"有車就有 上完就瞓<br />\n架車幾長有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c47d9ca4eeb66c6ac1220023a18d42c472b932","tid":982335,"uid":15660,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T19:05:02.000Z","msg":"On99"}]}